schema.description:
SSE stream with events: token, metadata, birthChart, done, error.

Example events:
```
event: token
data: {"text": "Based on your"}

event: token
data: {"text": " birth chart,"}

event: metadata
data: {"model": "Vedika AI", "processing_time_ms": 2340}

event: birthChart
data: {"ascendant": {"sign": "Libra", "degree": 15.42}, ...}

event: done
data: {"conversationId": "conv_abc123"}
```
